    {
      "id": "PopularPost258455",
      "post_content": "This card is so much fun!  \n  \n[Leyline of the Void](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of the Void) (or [Wheel of Sun and Moon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wheel of Sun and Moon)) stops opponents from giving it away. [Leyline of Sanctity](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Sanctity) (or [Runed Halo](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Runed Halo), [True Believer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=True Believer), [Solitary Confinement](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Solitary Confinement), [Witchbane Orb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Witchbane Orb), [Spirit of the Hearth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spirit of the Hearth), or, even better in team games, [Imperial Mask](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Imperial Mask)) stops opponents from giving it back to you. And even if they did manage to give it back, any instant will stamp it with a big, red, \"return to sender\" label and blow it up right in their face.  \n  \nHowever, I think I prefer [Sundial of the Infinite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sundial of the Infinite) to skip the trigger, then [Silence](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Silence) during their upkeep. And maybe [Copy Enchantment](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Copy Enchantment) and/or [Replenish](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Replenish)/[Auramancer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Auramancer) to go the distance?  \n  \nI really want to include some sort of instant-speed ... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Ragamander",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost258455\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">This card is so much fun!<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Leyline of the Void\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of the Void\">Leyline of the Void</a> (or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wheel of Sun and Moon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wheel of Sun and Moon\">Wheel of Sun and Moon</a>) stops opponents from giving it away.  <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Leyline of Sanctity\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Sanctity\">Leyline of Sanctity</a> (or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Runed Halo\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Runed Halo\">Runed Halo</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"True Believer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=True Believer\">True Believer</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Solitary Confinement\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Solitary Confinement\">Solitary Confinement</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Witchbane Orb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Witchbane Orb\">Witchbane Orb</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spirit of the Hearth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spirit of the Hearth\">Spirit of the Hearth</a>, or, even better in team games, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Imperial Mask\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Imperial Mask\">Imperial Mask</a>) stops opponents from giving it back to you.  And even if they did manage to give it back, any instant will stamp it with a big, red, \"return to sender\" label and blow it up right in their face.<br/><br/>However, I think I prefer <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sundial of the Infinite\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sundial of the Infinite\">Sundial of the Infinite</a> to skip the trigger, then <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Silence\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Silence\">Silence</a> during their upkeep. And maybe <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Copy Enchantment\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Copy Enchantment\">Copy Enchantment</a> and/or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Replenish\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Replenish\">Replenish</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Auramancer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Auramancer\">Auramancer</a> to go the distance?<br/><br/>I really want to include some sort of instant-speed <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=\"></a>... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 258455)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '258455'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy13722\">Ragamander</span>\r\n                                (7/19/2012 6:43:17 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Rig