    {
      "id": "PopularPost299361",
      "post_content": "Really unique card  \n  \nSome fun ways to use it  \n  \nDuress/Despise cards they can actually cast out of their hands  \n[Pyrostatic Pillar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyrostatic Pillar) or [Polluted Bonds](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Polluted Bonds) so that they lose life by playing stuff anyway",
      "posted_by": "feedbacker",
